Important Disclaimers:

Penny stocks (<$5/share) are highly volatile, speculative, and risky. Many are micro-caps with low liquidity.
"Current" based on recent market data (e.g., Oct 2024); prices change rapidly—check Yahoo Finance, Nasdaq, or OTC Markets.
Categories are interpretive: "Military" = defense; "Educational" limited options; "Cybernetics" = robotics/AI/cyber fusion (few pure plays).
Not financial advice. Do your own research (DYOR). Past performance ≠ future results. Consult a professional. Some trade OTC (riskier). Losses possible.
